{"tid":905072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被告顏力光用蜜糖樽從後襲擊死者，而死者的致命傷在後腦及頸項，故仍控告顏謀殺","createTime":"2018-11-17T00:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T03:10:54.000Z","uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cf510698eb0fd833f888f8d14571424c6d6f7a1c","tid":905072,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:09:33.000Z","msg":"中秋佳節本應人月兩圓，但兩批人在歡慶佳節時卻因醉酒鬧事釀成悲劇，為所有人帶來不能彌補的遺憾。前年迎月夜石澳大浪灣發生毆鬥命案，兩班消遣飲酒作樂的人為播歌瑣事爭執，繼而動武，結果一名廣告公司職員被人圍毆重傷，復遭利剪插入後腦喪命。警方事後控告五人傷人及謀殺等罪，經兩個月審訊後，其中三人昨被判罪成，當中一名任工程師的被告更因謀殺被判終身監禁。但無論判決如何，都已不能挽回慘劇中失去的一條寶貴生命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方昨指，根據案發地點的閉路電視錄影帶，被告顏力光用蜜糖樽從後襲擊死者，而死者的致命傷在後腦及頸項，故仍控告顏謀殺，其餘四人全改控蓄意傷人罪。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，案發日晚上11時半，死者與友人在大浪灣燒烤場燒烤，而涉案被告一幫人等則在滑浪店外飲酒。疑因滑浪店傳出的音樂聲量太大，雙方起爭執並發生打鬥。其後死者離開燒烤場時，突遭人從後用硬物襲擊後腦及頸項，以致嚴重出血。有目擊者報警，警方到場發現死者躺在血泊中，其他人則逃去無蹤。"},{"pid":"3928bbf886f03276901ed1f670ee4b750e17883e","tid":905072,"uid":3647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:30:41.000Z","msg":"有燒烤叉唔用 用痴立立既蜜糖樽"},{"pid":"99bea00820b734f3941251991c2945fbf962b4a2","tid":905072,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"勇武呀嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d838588bd33cb2435820ec08cca3736e6e1f42e0","tid":905072,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剪刀呢?"},{"pid":"b12527037ec6e4f2b00f0e2df3ac340120e69092","tid":905072,"uid":92859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"蜜糖樽下死 做鬼也心甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e02c7191370b11118854c2e7e362127c12045e7","tid":905072,"uid":19660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"咁利剪到底有冇用到"},{"pid":"dc5cc13a70cf5c127d5b6cd6ad4a4b4b008fa0e1","tid":905072,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12527037ec6e4f2b00f0e2df3ac340120e69092","tid":905072,"uid":92859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"蜜糖樽下死 做鬼也心甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"成頭蜜糖咁返黎報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9de81551b8a9d4fcbc6b51c505776405d16408d","tid":905072,"uid":164372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"成十年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38aecac88191384491e4aabf5702cfcba97638fc","tid":905072,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5cc13a70cf5c127d5b6cd6ad4a4b4b008fa0e1","tid":905072,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12527037ec6e4f2b00f0e2df3ac340120e69092","tid":905072,"uid":92859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"蜜糖樽下死 做鬼也心甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"成頭蜜糖咁返黎報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bd4428eecc853ceb3b11957f51b6c409837cfb","tid":905072,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"終身監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}